# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2024-04-28

### 🎉 Initial Release

#### 🏗️ Infrastructure Setup
- Traefik as reverse proxy with automatic SSL certificates
- Cloudflare Tunnel integration for secure external access
- Authentik Single Sign-On (SSO) implementation
- Docker Compose based deployment
- Network segmentation and security considerations

#### 🚀 Services Included
- **Authentication**: Authentik
- **Reverse Proxy**: Traefik
- **External Access**: Cloudflared
- **Dashboard**: Homepage
- **Documentation**: Outline Wiki
- **Git Services**: Gitea + Drone CI
- **Recipe Management**: Mealie
- **Notifications**: 
  - Gotify
  - NTFY
- **Monitoring Stack**:
  - Grafana
  - Prometheus
  - Node Exporter
  - cAdvisor
- **Database**: PostgreSQL + pgAdmin
- **Caching**: Redis + RedisInsight

#### ⚙️ Configuration Requirements
- Docker Engine 24.0+
- Docker Compose v2.21+
- Domain name with DNS access
- Cloudflare account
- Minimum 4GB RAM
- 20GB available storage
- Linux-based OS (tested on Ubuntu 22.04)

#### 📚 Documentation
- Comprehensive README
- Environment variables examples
- Security considerations
- Quick start guide
- Architecture diagram